{"tid":1442853,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"乜撚野警黑合作? 而家係政黑勾結!","createTime":"2019-08-11T05:27:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T05:56:17.000Z","uid":42431,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eb2f4ffd236a5a6b1f56ddf372b9f19661ecd8e9","tid":1442853,"uid":42431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:27:02.000Z","msg":"首先大家都明三權分立已經名存實亡<br />\n<br />\n721黑警刻意放生白衫人<br />\n中聯辦葉虎事件揭露政權都有份參與<br />\n律政司遲遲唔起訴捉到既白衫人<br />\n<br />\n每件事都係話你知三權分立已死<br />\n借用一下巴打張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[日式圖解] 721恐襲關係圖，推到發夢都睇到<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1442677\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1442677</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UGxWhu2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUGxWhu2.png&h=875a2776&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我見大家仲講緊警黑合作, 首先淨係講警察錯, 好多人仲會覺得唔關政府事, 你要打就打到佢冚家剷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 要表達到 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">政府、律政司、黑警 都有同 黑社會勾結</span><br />\n<br />\n第二係你咪撚再用<span style=\"color: blue;\">合作</span>咁正面既詞語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 而家佢地係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">勾結</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 你講合作講到佢地好似有正當性可以咁做<br />\n<br />\n我在此強烈呼籲大家唔好再講警黑合作, 試著說<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政黑勾結</span></span>"},{"pid":"03bf916c325d5ebe06be10ba7d3181dd84550564","tid":1442853,"uid":42431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:29:38.000Z","msg":"721元朗恐襲 政黑勾結殘害無辜市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3ac6455866c762a8200327f8b3792efc37841eb","tid":1442853,"uid":42431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:30:32.000Z","msg":"721元朗恐襲 政黑勾結殘害無辜市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a36ce37fe06d8925ddd690007c3759819f32ace","tid":1442853,"uid":42431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:32:46.000Z","msg":"721元朗恐襲 政黑勾結殘害無辜市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"564058f7969c2eb4c5e7d619abf7287a25ad42c3","tid":1442853,"uid":42431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:32:48.000Z","msg":"721元朗恐襲 政黑勾結殘害無辜市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840384532c77d8107d652f4f33d25f650234c0cd","tid":1442853,"uid":42431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:37:24.000Z","msg":"721元朗恐襲 政黑勾結殘害無辜市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"794639196477d3cffc4b2a78bd65e89f9ff31086","tid":1442853,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:39:22.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">721元朗恐襲</span></strong></span></div><br />\n警黑合作 警署落閘<br />\n999唔通 無人落charge<br />\n<br />\n721元朗恐襲第22日<br />\n無人落charge <br />\n無警停職<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無忘721<br />\n記者請日日追問插問</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家copy and paste pls<br />\n每日改第xx日<br />\n<br />\nKeep push to keep this at the top!</span></span>"},{"pid":"11e1fe4e9b9fe58dd1c53fd9d582a20a757d9f38","tid":1442853,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af6648c84640d0d98c66cddbcabcfd10d5fa86ef","tid":1442853,"uid":42431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:54:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政黑勾結</span></span>"},{"pid":"6488c8dc29b777f7049c35cb7cf802ee2ac7810a","tid":1442